posts.title: I just got my mic arm and I'm super proud that I managed to get my first ever setup done to the point where I'm happy with it.
posts.description: Some context. I'm on disability and I've been making due for most of my time. But I've not had any funds to improve my setup. Luckily a charity that grants funds for people with longtime disabilities approved my application and funded me the mic in the photo and a pair of Audio-Technica ATH-M50X headphones! And I managed to save up for the Roadworx Microphone Arm, completing my setup!
